{"title":"冲锋号（外二首）——当年的诗传单","authors":["田间"],"dates":[{"year":1983,"month":9,"day":23}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"冲锋号（外二首）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——当年的诗传单"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"田　间"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"听，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大山欢笑。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"听，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"巨石呼啸。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"壮士正年少，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"肩担红霞照。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看东方大地，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"此时已拂晓。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那千里征途，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"任我辈跨跃。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那花般岁月，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"必将来到！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"仇　恨"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"岩上那一枝野花，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"映照衣衫上血痕。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大颗血滴正沉吟，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那是女孩子的眼睛。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有人问她的姓名？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"她只喊一声“仇恨”。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是她拉响地雷，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"挡住敌人前进。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"仇恨长在哪里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哪里便有花藤。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"她随雷声运行，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"此刻仍有回声……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"太行之子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"炸弹挂在树上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"树也就是刀叉。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"地雷埋在山上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"石头也起火花。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"太行山是铁壁，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"到处流传佳话。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我是太行之子，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就在你身边长大。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"望见你那雄姿——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我愿忘记年已花甲……"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}